# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the values.

## Required

```env
# Database connection string
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://devroast:devroast_local_dev@localhost:5432/devroast
```

## Optional

```env
# OpenAI API key for AI-powered code roasting
# Get your key from https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=
```

## Development

For local development with Docker:

```bash
# Start PostgreSQL
docker compose up -d

# Push schema to database
npm run db:push
```

For testing AI features, add your OpenAI API key to `.env.local`.